**       KANBAN NAME
CPLATING KANBAN
DTUNNEL KANBAN
EPICK-UP KANBAN
0CMPLET PART KANBAN
**       ERROR MESSAGE
E-01 WHEN DON'T USE IT LONG TIME SIGN  OFF.
E-02 INPUT UPDATE INSTRUCTION
E-03 UPDATE INSTRUCTION ONLY 0,1,2.
E-04 INPUT INTRAL COMPANY PART NO
E-05 THIS P/N OF PART M/F ISN'T INPUT SO THAT CAN'T UPDATE
E-06 THIS P/N OF PART M/F IS NOT VOLUME PRODUCTION INPUT
E-07 THIS P/N IS INPUT INTO INTRAL COMPANY KANBAN CHANGE M/F
E-08 THE LAST KANBAN KIND OF THIS P/N  BESIDES "C" - "E"
E-09 APPOINTED CHANGE OR CANCEL THIS PART NO ISN'T INPUT
E-10 APPOINTED CHANGE OR CANCEL THIS PART NO IS CANCELLED
E-11 ADD WAS APPOINTED THIS PART NO IS REGISTERED ALREADY.
E-12 INPUT DATE OF START PRODUCTION
E-13 DATE OF START PRODUCTION ISN'T RIGHT
E-14 INPUT KANBAN EFFECTIVE DAY
E-15 EFFECTIVE KANBAN DAY ISN'T RIGHT
E-16 BECAUSE LARGE KANBAN KIND IS <0.E>,INPUT PRE PROC CYCLE
E-17 INPUT PRECEDING PROCESS PROCESSING CYCLE REVERSING
E-18 BECAUSE KANBAN (L) IS <0.E>, CAN'T INPUT PLATING CYCLE
E-19 BECAUSE KANBAN (L) IS <0.E>, CAN'T INPUT 2ND CYCLE
E-20 BECAUSE KANBAN (L) IS C, INPUT PRECEDING PROCESS CYCLE
E-21 BECAUSE KANBAN (L) IS C, INPUT PLATING CYCLE
E-22 PRE PROC DEPT CODE IS NOT INPUT BUT ROUTE IS INPUT
E-23 PRE PROC DEPT CODE IS INPUT  BUT ROUTE IS NOT
E-24 PRE PROC DEPT CODE ISN'T INPUT BUT SPECIAL BIN IS INPUT
E-25 PLATING DEPT CODE ISN'T INPUT BUT ROUTE IS INPUT
